PUT IN BUILD SCRIPT:

TO SEE WHAT'S NOT DONE:

ruby NEW/nokogiri_cll.rb html NEW/source_small_1_coverage.xml 2>&1 >\!~/www/media/public/tmp/sc1.html  | grep '^DEF'
ruby NEW/nokogiri_cll.rb latex NEW/source_small_1_coverage.xml 2>&1 >\!build/sc1.tex | grep '^DEF'  ; cd build/ ; xelatex sc1.tex ; xelatex sc1.tex ; xelatex sc1.tex ; cp sc1.pdf ~/www/media/public/tmp

DOCUMENT targets:

NEW/target_small_1_coverage_latex.tex
NEW/target_small_1_coverage_nochunks_xhtml.html

ruby ../NEW/nokogiri_cll.rb latex ../NEW/source_small_1_coverage.xml >\!sc1.tex ; xelatex sc1.tex ; xelatex sc1.tex ; xelatex sc1.tex ; cp sc1.pdf ~/www/media/public/tmp
ruby ../NEW/nokogiri_cll.rb html ../NEW/source_small_1_coverage.xml >\!~/www/media/public/tmp/sc1.html

<valsi>bridi</valsi> links to glossary entries

